{"tid":1744094,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(推上去)話你知點解手足會被捕被毒打，要困喺埋大","createTime":"2019-11-21T13:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T07:22:21.000Z","uid":137109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ff715a4a4df4defd4b8bb5ba5f1c18e73d58f60b","tid":1744094,"uid":137109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:57:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為香港人唔會自願罷工 下下要勇武行前多幾步承受極大風險</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n解決辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 成立/加入工會 聚集各工各業手足 凝聚力量互相守護  (叫咗好耐都係6萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />另外194萬去咗邊)<br />\nTg: <a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt813VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=781cf06d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\nFb: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2JQLM2f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JQLM2f&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt813VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=ffee1401\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2JQLM2f</a><br />\nIG: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/33hmGRR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33hmGRR&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt813VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=a061c49b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/33hmGRR</a><br />\n<br />\n大三罷成功嘅必要條件: <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">歷時長，規模大 </span></strong><br />\n正苦唯一春袋=經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ncondom嘅犧牲對佢亳無價值<br />\n<br />\n點解要入公會?: 消除囚犯兩難問題 絕大部分香港人如果冇保障下唔敢為抗爭付出過多<br />\n睇下呢個post: <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1698589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1698589</a><br />\n<br />\n公會並非大台 作用為提供平台凝聚手足力量 支援因罷工而付出代價嘅手足 (正如星火, 守護孩子)<br />\n<br />\n大三罷成功嘅必要條件: 歷時長，規模大 <br />\n終極目標為<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">長久癱瘓香港經濟嘅極大規模罷工，以換取五大訴求 爭取有公義嘅社會 淸算黑警</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(單日而規模細嘅話=山竹 政權不痛不癢 翌日如常)<br />\n大大力鍊落去政權個經濟春袋度 機場可以出禁制令 對罷工唯一對策係拖 以真攬炒逼使五大訴求實現）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n迷思1: <br />\n學生罷課冇意義<br />\nAns: 大學生明白背後理念 應該出力遊説 打破同溫層 更可以幫手籌備/宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再者 試諗下基層一個清潔工覺得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">手停口停</span></strong></span> 因此唔參加一定要幫手教育recruit (除咗五大訴求 唔一定以政治目標recruit同路人 其實社會一直有更多不公義 例如外判制剝削員工福利 其他勞工保障 樓價等世界之巔 無能而冇認受性政府一直視之不見)<br />\n(應屆dse都要兼顧學業 大學唔可以冇你哋)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n迷思2: <br />\n身邊冇咩人罷所以我收皮<br />\nAns: 你收皮就香港收皮 你罷就感染身邊人一齊罷 情況好似滾雪球 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一個department過半數人罷=全公司被罷工</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n迷思3: <br />\n做咩都冇用<br />\nAns: 義士唔係condom 連你都唔肯幫手經濟抗爭 香港就只剩冷漠自私功利嘅人 唔洗再奢望有公民社會<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">未聽過香港有餓死嘅人 只有被黑警打死/鳩拉嘅手足</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n迷思4: <br />\n我有包袱<br />\nAns: 義士都有屋企人㗎！呢個仆街政府屠殺平民你可以袖手旁觀咩? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢6個月有冇喊 失眠 無力過? 請用你嘅行動驅散負面情緒 光復香港唔止係口號 更加係每位嘅責任<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3065b2e33dae22231cee75010ab68b8b8e3017","tid":1744094,"uid"